title_bed_bats_review: Bed and breakfast in Dhaka · ★New · 2 bedrooms · 1 private bath
listing_description:
Featuring free WiFi and a restaurant, Hotel Ornate offers accommodation in Dhaka. Free private parking is available on site.

Rooms come with a TV with satellite channels. Rooms have a private bathroom. Extras include slippers and free toiletries.

There is a 24-hour front desk offering express check-in/check-out services, a business centre, hairdresser's, and gift shop at the property.

Guests can approach the tour desk staff to plan a day trip or for car rental arrangement.
